{"tid":1949020,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我會打定輸數","createTime":"2020-03-29T11:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T12:21:09.000Z","uid":29052,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"125b3f9495b37efbe3743aaf33debd948af8b413","tid":1949020,"uid":29052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:12:26.000Z","msg":"我會暫時成為你嘅避風塘 暫時都還有我在<br />\n耐性地舔著你的傷。<br />\n<br />\n直到你療癒或者佢搵返你<br />\n無論你最後選擇係點 我會再有任何怨言 <br />\n因為我知道我唔係最好 <br />\n而我遇見你已經係好幸福<br />\n<br />\n你在想誰想到睡不著<br />\n你應該覺得驕傲<br />\n很多人想失戀也沒有目標<br />\n只是想睡個好覺 別炫耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n扮偉大嘅我其實好自私 只係想用盡一切方法 去換取你嘅開心 所以到最後如果冇揀我 唔洗感覺對我有虧欠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084f1cc2d880aa4019cc2cedab456c20ce568c6a","tid":1949020,"uid":29052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"叫下蠢姐！"},{"pid":"0e817b2720ad4d14c53f67554337ee3b9054676e","tid":1949020,"uid":29052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947d2594ef2511741690cf66be0da34aa662e141","tid":1949020,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賤過隻狗"},{"pid":"7452cc493955cc2cf7320357aeeaefd44af888f7","tid":1949020,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"樓主加油"},{"pid":"18ef9a70173872eff153bc065d3c0508370282c8","tid":1949020,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:12:28.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"bde9a294ad88deea5718462c0b6fcb6ada1ab7ea","tid":1949020,"uid":29052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"吹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac